{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":825,"text":"The school of architecture\nthat I studied at some 30 years ago"},{"time":5179,"text":"happened to be across the street\nfrom the wonderful art gallery"},{"time":9042,"text":"designed by the great\narchitect Louis Kahn."},{"time":13157,"text":"I love the building,\nand I used to visit it quite often."},{"time":16894,"text":"One day,"},{"time":18449,"text":"I saw the security guard run his hand\nacross the concrete wall."},{"time":25032,"text":"And it was the way he did it,"},{"time":26788,"text":"the expression on his face --"},{"time":29434,"text":"something touched me."},{"time":32081,"text":"I could see that the security guard\nwas moved by the building"},{"time":37691,"text":"and that architecture has that capacity"},{"time":41853,"text":"to move you."},{"time":43529,"text":"I could see it, and I remember thinking,"},{"time":45980,"text":"\"Wow. How does architecture do that?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":51355,"text":"At school, I was learning to design,"},{"time":55555,"text":"but here -- here was\na reaction of the heart."},{"time":59959,"text":"And it touched me to the core."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65529,"text":"You know, you aspire for beauty,"},{"time":71310,"text":"for sensuousness, for atmosphere,\nthe emotional response."},{"time":77730,"text":"That's the realm of the ineffable"},{"time":80286,"text":"and the immeasurable."},{"time":82081,"text":"And that's what you live for:"},{"time":84971,"text":"a chance to try."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87858,"text":"So in 2003, there was\nan open call for designs"},{"time":91359,"text":"for the Bahá'í Temple for South America."},{"time":93505,"text":"This was the first temple\nin all of South America."},{"time":96527,"text":"It's a continental temple,"},{"time":98435,"text":"a hugely important milestone\nfor the Bahá'í community,"},{"time":101638,"text":"because this would be the last\nof the continental temples"},{"time":105894,"text":"and would open the door\nfor national and local temples to be built"},{"time":109474,"text":"around the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110823,"text":"And the brief was deceptively simple"},{"time":114397,"text":"and unique in the annals of religion:"},{"time":119062,"text":"a circular room, nine sides,\nnine entrances, nine paths,"},{"time":126036,"text":"allowing you to come to the temple\nfrom all directions,"},{"time":131542,"text":"nine symbolizing completeness,"},{"time":134500,"text":"perfection."},{"time":136526,"text":"No pulpit, no sermons,"},{"time":140064,"text":"as there are no clergy\nin the Bahá'í faith."},{"time":143010,"text":"And in a world which is putting up walls,"},{"time":147139,"text":"the design needed to express in form"},{"time":150611,"text":"the very opposite."},{"time":153079,"text":"It had to be open, welcoming"},{"time":157051,"text":"to people of all faiths,\nwalks of life, backgrounds,"},{"time":161619,"text":"or no faith at all;"},{"time":164343,"text":"a new form of sacred space"},{"time":167656,"text":"with no pattern"},{"time":170654,"text":"or models to draw from."},{"time":174328,"text":"It was like designing one of the first\nchurches for Christianity"},{"time":178210,"text":"or one of the first mosques for Islam."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182049,"text":"So we live in a secular world."},{"time":188579,"text":"How do you design sacred space today?"},{"time":194298,"text":"And how do you even define\nwhat's sacred today?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":201003,"text":"I stumbled across this beautiful quote\nfrom the Bahá'í writings,"},{"time":206001,"text":"and it speaks to prayer."},{"time":209432,"text":"It says that if you reach out in prayer,"},{"time":212931,"text":"and if your prayer is answered --\nwhich is already very interesting --"},{"time":216699,"text":"that the pillars of your heart\nwill become ashine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222296,"text":"And I loved this idea\nof the inner and the outer,"},{"time":225948,"text":"like when you see someone\nand you say, \"That person is radiant.\""},{"time":232179,"text":"And I was thinking, \"My gosh,\nhow could we make something"},{"time":237235,"text":"architectural out of that,"},{"time":239322,"text":"where you create a building"},{"time":243551,"text":"and it becomes alive with light?"},{"time":247522,"text":"Like alabaster, if you kiss it with light,\nit becomes alive."},{"time":251564,"text":"And I drew this sketch,"},{"time":253730,"text":"something with two layers, translucent"},{"time":257115,"text":"with structure in between capturing light."},{"time":260646,"text":"Maybe a pure form,\na single form of emanation"},{"time":266631,"text":"that you could imagine"},{"time":269076,"text":"would be all dome"},{"time":272604,"text":"and everything we kept making\nwas looking too much like an egg."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276099,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":277733,"text":"A blob."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279706,"text":"So you search."},{"time":281529,"text":"You all know this crazy search,\nletting the process take you,"},{"time":286056,"text":"and you live for the surprises."},{"time":287704,"text":"And I remember quite by accident"},{"time":289954,"text":"I saw this little video\nof a plant moving in light,"},{"time":295350,"text":"and it made me think of movement,"},{"time":299037,"text":"reach,"},{"time":300233,"text":"this idea that the temple\ncould have reach,"},{"time":302573,"text":"like this reach for the divine."},{"time":305407,"text":"You can imagine also"},{"time":307256,"text":"that movement within a circle\ncould mean movement and stillness,"},{"time":312175,"text":"like the cosmos,"},{"time":314190,"text":"something you see in many places."}]},{"cues":[{"time":317885,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":320311,"text":"But rotation was not enough,"},{"time":324848,"text":"because we needed a form."},{"time":327056,"text":"In the Bahá'í writings, it talks about"},{"time":329346,"text":"the temples being as perfect\nas is humanly possible,"},{"time":334232,"text":"and we kept thinking,\nwell, what is perfection?"},{"time":336833,"text":"And I remember I stumbled into this image\nof this Japanese basket"},{"time":341201,"text":"and thinking our Western notions\nof perfection need to be challenged,"},{"time":345226,"text":"that this wonderful silhouette\nof this basket, this wonkiness,"},{"time":349973,"text":"and that it has the kind of dimple\nof what you might imagine a shoulder"},{"time":355645,"text":"or the cheekbone,"},{"time":357176,"text":"and that kind of organic form."},{"time":360053,"text":"And so we drew and made models,"},{"time":362890,"text":"these lines that merge at the top,"},{"time":366129,"text":"soft lines,"},{"time":368487,"text":"which became like drapery"},{"time":371452,"text":"and translucent veils and folding,"},{"time":374973,"text":"and the idea of not only\nfolding but torquing --"},{"time":379087,"text":"you remember the plant\nand the way it was reaching."},{"time":382917,"text":"And this started to become\nan interesting form,"},{"time":386580,"text":"carving the base, making the entrances."}]},{"cues":[{"time":389976,"text":"And then we ended up with this."},{"time":392123,"text":"This is this temple with two layers,"},{"time":395744,"text":"nine luminous veils,"},{"time":398261,"text":"embodied light,"},{"time":399760,"text":"soft-flowing lines"},{"time":401731,"text":"like luminescent drapery."},{"time":403918,"text":"180 submissions\nwere received from 80 countries,"},{"time":408011,"text":"and this was selected."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410042,"text":"So we went to the next stage\nof how to build it."},{"time":416031,"text":"We had submitted alabaster."},{"time":420115,"text":"But alabaster was too soft,"},{"time":422669,"text":"and we were experimenting,\nmany experiments with materials,"},{"time":426169,"text":"trying to think how we could have\nthis kind of shimmer,"},{"time":430592,"text":"and we ended up with borosilicate."},{"time":433640,"text":"And borosilicate glass,\nas you know, is very strong,"},{"time":437240,"text":"and if you break borosilicate rods\njust so and melt them"},{"time":442490,"text":"at just the right temperature,"},{"time":444818,"text":"we ended up with this new material,"},{"time":446610,"text":"this new cast glass which took us\nabout two years to make."},{"time":451758,"text":"And it had this quality that we loved,"},{"time":454085,"text":"this idea of the embodied light,"},{"time":457156,"text":"but on the inside, we wanted\nsomething with a soft light,"},{"time":461510,"text":"like the inner lining of a jacket."},{"time":464145,"text":"On the outside you have protection,\nbut on the inside you touch it."},{"time":468805,"text":"So we found this tiny vein\nin a huge quarry in Portugal"},{"time":474644,"text":"with this beautiful stone,"},{"time":477951,"text":"which the owner had kept\nfor seven generations in his family,"},{"time":482985,"text":"waiting for the right project,\nif you can believe it."},{"time":487877,"text":"Look at this material, it's beautiful."},{"time":489993,"text":"And the way it lights up;\nit has that translucent quality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494404,"text":"So here you see the structure."},{"time":497173,"text":"It lets the light through."},{"time":499509,"text":"And looking down,"},{"time":503195,"text":"the nine wings are bound,"},{"time":505491,"text":"structurally but symbolically strong,"},{"time":509055,"text":"a great symbol of unity:"},{"time":512553,"text":"pure geometry, a perfect circle,"},{"time":515650,"text":"30 meters in section and in plan,"},{"time":520060,"text":"perfectly symmetrical,"},{"time":521864,"text":"like the idea of sacredness and geometry."},{"time":525992,"text":"And here you see the building going up,"},{"time":529172,"text":"2,000 steel nodes,"},{"time":531483,"text":"9,000 pieces of steel,"},{"time":535197,"text":"7,800 stone pieces,"},{"time":538009,"text":"10,000 cast glass pieces,\nall individual shapes,"},{"time":542565,"text":"the entire superstructure all described,"},{"time":545622,"text":"engineered, fabricated\nwith aerospace technology,"},{"time":550137,"text":"prefabricated machine to machine,"},{"time":553348,"text":"robotically,"},{"time":555236,"text":"a huge team effort, you can imagine,"},{"time":557537,"text":"of literally hundreds,"},{"time":559505,"text":"and within three percent\nof our $30 million budget"},{"time":564257,"text":"set in 2006."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566564,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":570081,"text":"Nine wings bound together"},{"time":575197,"text":"forming a nine-pointed star,"},{"time":578940,"text":"and the star shape moving in space,"},{"time":583367,"text":"tracking the sun."}]},{"cues":[{"time":595762,"text":"So here it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597226,"text":"Audience: Wow!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":599801,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":607986,"text":"Hopefully, a befitting response\nto that beautiful quote,"},{"time":613386,"text":"\"a prayer answered,\""},{"time":615546,"text":"open in all directions,"},{"time":618773,"text":"capturing the blue light of dawn,"},{"time":622233,"text":"tent-like white light of day,"},{"time":625940,"text":"the gold light of the afternoon,"},{"time":628882,"text":"and of course, at night, the reversal:"},{"time":633482,"text":"sensuous,"},{"time":636371,"text":"catching the light in all kinds\nof mysterious ways."}]},{"cues":[{"time":641583,"text":"And the site: it's interesting;\n14 years ago when we made the submission,"},{"time":647218,"text":"we showed the temple\nset against the Andes."},{"time":649352,"text":"We didn't have the Andes as our site,"},{"time":653705,"text":"but after nine years, that's exactly\nwhere we ended up,"},{"time":658527,"text":"the lines of the temple set against\nnothing but pure nature,"},{"time":662015,"text":"and you turn around and you get\nnothing but the city below you,"},{"time":667178,"text":"and inside, a view in all directions,"},{"time":673105,"text":"radiating gardens"},{"time":675760,"text":"from each of the alcoves,"},{"time":679457,"text":"radiating paths."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684150,"text":"Last October, the opening ceremonies --"},{"time":688846,"text":"a beautiful, sacred event,"},{"time":692631,"text":"5,000 people from 80 countries,"},{"time":695682,"text":"a continuous river of visitors,"},{"time":699619,"text":"indigenous people\nfrom all over South America,"},{"time":703113,"text":"some who had never left their villages."},{"time":707283,"text":"And of course, that this temple\nbelongs to people,"},{"time":711805,"text":"the collective, of many cultures\nand walks of life,"},{"time":717264,"text":"many beliefs,"},{"time":718704,"text":"and for me, what's most important\nis what it feels like on the inside;"},{"time":723341,"text":"that it feel intimate,"},{"time":726191,"text":"sacred,"},{"time":727970,"text":"and that everyone is welcome."},{"time":730374,"text":"And if even a few who come"},{"time":735017,"text":"have the same reaction\nas that security guard,"},{"time":739884,"text":"then it truly would be their temple."},{"time":745242,"text":"And I would love that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":746867,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":748065,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}